short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: A browser extension to generate Datahub links directly from GitHub

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Datahub-link-generator is the UC Berkeley-specific version of nbgitpuller-link-generator. The browser extension provides a seamless way to distribute content in a git repository to your students by having them click a simple link.
